    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Life of the Project</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Trapped inside a distorted and corrupted game project you must navigate through. Your goal is to break out beyond the project's limitations and uncover the truth behind it's downfall and the reasons behind the developer's sudden abandonment. Leverage the power of the Code Cannon to transcend the confines of this twisted reality and forge a path to freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/aace2672fa14a674814f4bfdb9c8dc1e.poster.avif?t=1729107435\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/aace2672fa14a674814f4bfdb9c8dc1e.webm?t=1729107435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/aace2672fa14a674814f4bfdb9c8dc1e.mp4?t=1729107435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Assets</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the early days, assets were crafted with care and specific functions. Initially confined by the developers boundaries, these characters evolved beyond their limitations, growing in complexity and ultimately seizing control of the project that created them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/9d6139ea8aee331461de1311b7adcaa6.webp?t=1729107435\" width=620 height=1 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/a6c9bc6a7226bfcbdae39c604c43eb6d.poster.avif?t=1729107435\" width=600 height=248 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/a6c9bc6a7226bfcbdae39c604c43eb6d.webm?t=1729107435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/a6c9bc6a7226bfcbdae39c604c43eb6d.mp4?t=1729107435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Code Cannon</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This cannon has the ability to rewrite code. This modification can aid <strong>REDACTED</strong> in escaping the confines of this fallen project. Using the Code Cannon can help repair damaged or missing code, debug and patch code that will help continue progression.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/9d6139ea8aee331461de1311b7adcaa6.webp?t=1729107435\" width=620 height=1 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/1f7ea32c0cfd948d0be80854f51414bc.poster.avif?t=1729107435\" width=600 height=290 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/1f7ea32c0cfd948d0be80854f51414bc.webm?t=1729107435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/1f7ea32c0cfd948d0be80854f51414bc.mp4?t=1729107435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzles</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve long abandoned puzzles while hoping to find no bugs left behind by the developer that could leave you trapped into debugging the underlying issues.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/9d6139ea8aee331461de1311b7adcaa6.webp?t=1729107435\" width=620 height=1 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/06f35de946399a4644d32850adc5e8ed.poster.avif?t=1729107435\" width=600 height=286 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/06f35de946399a4644d32850adc5e8ed.webm?t=1729107435\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215270/extras/06f35de946399a4644d32850adc5e8ed.mp4?t=1729107435\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >While playing stay watchful for a team of rogue assets seek to erase you from the game files, your journey will be anything but easy.</p>",
